{"tid":1586674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（玩出火）AREA 51 出動坦克","createTime":"2019-09-22T05:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T05:44:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1fc9afa847beac3ff31890bd6f9479c12c47a7cc","tid":1586674,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/21/ya4Ngk.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F21%2Fya4Ngk.jpeg&h=a98997f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\r\n美國網友日前發起活動，號召群眾前往傳聞有外星生命秘密的美軍設施「51區」（Area51），讓超過200萬人聲稱將會出席，引起當局關注且提出強烈警告，使得該活動變成2場「外星人慶典」，而活動地點就在離51區附近的小鎮舉辦。不過有外傳將有群眾將擅闖51區內，讓當局警方趕緊加派人員戒備，目前傳出至少有2人遭被拘捕後釋放。"},{"pid":"b0f6a1031c4170b624320459b14e4df8064c9c56","tid":1586674,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:30:39.000Z","msg":"Twitter 琴日傳緊呢張相係無坦克既"},{"pid":"545c96786187dae99d1369e3a0d4bc72f6ed6365","tid":1586674,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:32:33.000Z","msg":"衝51區有賞 情色明星將提供「服務」滿足UFO迷<br />\n<br />\n情色明星愛麗絲(Alice Little)將在內華達州舉辦一場非常「特殊」的活動滿足這些UFO迷。這項活動被命名為「Alienstock」，內容包含了「被外星人綁架」、「親密接觸」等等，而且活動還告知說若有參加衝「51區」的參與者將會給他們50%的折扣。<br />\n<br />\n我都有d想衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6fdad35ceda0b3a8cc7d229a36ab51d181a0cb","tid":1586674,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:33:05.000Z","msg":"美軍：你地現正參與一場非法集結，請你地立即離開，否則美軍會使用武力將你地驅散。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963e2c490ad9a6f17532696e187e5b86e195e817","tid":1586674,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:33:35.000Z","msg":"人地衝軍營比人捉完就放<br />\n香港喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a34af69877e13357ce70b0a5cd407b7992016be","tid":1586674,"uid":107023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:36:06.000Z","msg":"香港都有51區"},{"pid":"d4cfb43233d54b0e484098da5a88db831df14c9b","tid":1586674,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:36:59.000Z","msg":"驚！美軍方推特 宣稱要用B-2轟炸機對付擅闖51區民眾<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2923141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2923141&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=8351d09e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2923141&h=5f938c37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2923141</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國民眾近來在網路上號召前往神秘的51區「到此一遊」，在臉書社群引起廣大回應，最後萬人響應一人到場，20日活動當天只有百餘人出現在目的地附近，美國軍方卻自己搞出大包，相關單位的官方推特竟宣稱要部署B-2幽靈戰略轟炸機對付闖進51區的民眾。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n據《路透》報導，美國國防視覺資訊發布服務單位（Defense Visual Information Distribution Service，DVIDS）20日在推特上發布了一則訊息：「如果千禧一代試圖突襲51區，那這就是他們最後會看到的東西（The last thing #Millennials will see if they attempt the #area51raid today）」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n在此條推特上還附有一張B-2幽靈戰略轟炸機的照片，暗指擅闖禁地的民眾將會被B-2解決。DVIDS不久後立即刪除爭議推特並鄭重道歉，強調這是管理帳戶的員工所發布的，絕非美國國防部的立場。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n事實上，20日的「突襲51區」活動氣氛相當歡樂，大約有150人在基地附近同歡，一些民眾還cosplay成外星人，只有少數人因為違反軍方規定被捕。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpZ2vBHs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpZ2vBHs.jpg&h=79b45c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n點解我會理解為基地內冇特別機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c79f6f6b094674b85357067e4e764a36f908b1","tid":1586674,"uid":103653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:42:07.000Z","msg":"目前傳出至少有2人遭被拘捕後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">釋放</span></span>。"},{"pid":"d1b24d54a7c038a11c1c6f83f831b6bf04ef5f7d","tid":1586674,"uid":279989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:44:05.000Z","msg":"如果真係有外星人野，晨早搬左去第二度啦！<br />\n全世界都知，比你係美帝政府會唔會咁撚蠢？？"}]}